casebody.data:
Thursday, July 31, 1997

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

94-2668. Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Shabazz.

IT IS ORDERED by this court, sua sponte, that Donald A. Shabazz, Attorney Registration No. 0024227, last known address in Cincinnati, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of November 8, 1995, to wit: failure to pay board costs in the amount of $377.49 on or before February 6, 1996, and failure to pay publication costs in the amount of $107.45 on or before August 6,1996.
